### 2. Code Group API — `/api/code-groups`
### =====================================================================

### 2-1. 코드그룹 목록 검색
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/code-groups/search
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

{
  "page": 1,
  "size": 20,
  "codeGroupId": "",
  "codeGroupName": "",
  "useYn": "",
  "status": ""
}

### 2-2. 코드그룹 상세 — POST + body (path variable 아님)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/code-groups/detail
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

{
  "codeGroupSeq": {{codeGroupSeq}}
}

### 2-3. 코드그룹 등록
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/code-groups/create
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

{
  "codeGroupId": "SAMPLE_GROUP",
  "codeGroupName": "샘플그룹",
  "description": "HTTP 샘플",
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "useYn": "Y",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "createId": "system",
  "createIp": "127.0.0.1"
}

### 2-4. 코드그룹 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/code-groups/update
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

{
  "codeGroupSeq": {{codeGroupSeq}},
  "codeGroupId": "SAMPLE_GROUP",
  "codeGroupName": "샘플그룹수정",
  "description": "수정 설명",
  "sortOrder": 2,
  "useYn": "Y",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "modifyId": "admin",
  "modifyIp": "127.0.0.1"
}

### 2-5. 코드그룹 삭제 — DELETE + JSON body
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/code-groups/delete
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}

{
  "codeGroupSeq": {{codeGroupSeq}},
  "modifyId": "admin",
  "modifyIp": "127.0.0.1"
}

### 2-6. 코드그룹 옵션 (드롭다운용)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/code-groups/options
Accept: {{json}}
Cookie: {{sessionCookie}}


